data.description: Located in the desirable Redbird Ranch subdivision, this beautiful single-story home offers a stylish living space and an unbeatable location! Enjoy living within 10 minutes of grocery stores, restaurants, and excellent schools, and a quick 30 minute drive to JBSA Lackland and Downtown San Antonio. Outdoor enthusiasts will find themselves in a dream location with Hendrick Arnold Nature Park, Government Canyon State Natural Area, and the Golf Club of Texas, all within easy reach. The opportunities for adventures are endless! As a resident of Redbird Ranch, you'll also have access to fantastic community amenities, including a sparkling pool, tennis courts, a clubhouse for gatherings and events, and a park with a well-maintained playground.    Inside, an open, light-filled layout connects the formal dining area to the modern eat-in kitchen adorned with granite countertops, a gas stove, a large center island, and stainless steel appliances. The generously-sized living room is perfect for relaxation and gatherings. Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom suite boasting an oversized walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with a separate tub, shower, and double vanity sinks. Head outside to discover a large, fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying the sunshine. The covered patio allows for year-round enjoyment!    Take advantage of this opportunity to live the Redbird Ranch lifestyle!
